\n全部速食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65daa0d1771ea25e28dab39a1f91aa2c5b7d58b6","tid":998693,"uid":54417,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"38c3e5b7a69b44b7c9d01a83e795e023c9705070","tid":998693,"uid":188310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:57:23.000Z","msg":"瑪奇英雄傳呢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:59:48.000Z","msg":"都好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係有豐富特色嘅遊戲 <br />\n但我鐘意瑪奇個種休閒感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c072a8047bf4c1faf25ab65f6bee17dac84d7f","tid":998693,"uid":128761,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:00:17.000Z","msg":"歷史上可以同瑪奇平起平坐廣度深度都高既OLG應該係得返魔獸世界<br />\n<br />\n唔講每個npc都有自己既頭像、音樂<br />\n唔講染色係瑪奇帶起、武器都有n種玩法<br />\n就算係主打生活輕鬆既瑪奇<br />\n打怪戰鬥既打擊感、自由度至今無人能及<br />\n<br />\n基本上冇咩遊戲打怪係唔似切豆腐<br />\n但瑪奇做到唔同怪物有唔同跑速<br />\n唔同技能有唔同既動作<br />\n比人打真係會飛起、擊退<br />\n<br />\n去到2018年既今日，d所謂出名既xx沙漠、劍x....就算係魔獸世界<br />\n打怪真實度連瑪奇車尾燈都睇唔到"},{"pid":"2387ec0dc943459241c93c17e00a2013644ac83d","tid":998693,"uid":118562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:21:55.000Z","msg":"瑪奇以前真心正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戰鬥系統要你用腦,技能一招克一招,要你睇隻怪d走動估佢用緊咩技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  bgm又係世界級,唔同場景唔同npc都有專屬bgm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 主線直情係世界第一,係一出完你會即刻想解晒佢而唔係為獎勵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但隻驚而家已經搞彎晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻手機驚都係hea住咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好掛住以前個個係賽城掛機等打野團個年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac642ac5243e53dcf9538d9efa77b48a07dbe5a","tid":998693,"uid":75218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:38:29.000Z","msg":"你玩緊隻假既瑪奇 新果隻出未"}